---
title: Quick Smokey Chicken, Haloumi & Roast Pumpkin Toss with Herbed Mayo & Spring Onion
description: Who doesn’t like a bit of char on their chicken? This one gets a generous coating of our specially crafted punchy Kiwi spice blend before it crisps up in the pan until golden. Finish it off with a bed of roasted veggies and top it off with golden haloumi and a sprinkling of crispy shallots for an outstanding pairing of flavours – without the sweat and tears.

*We’ve replaced the crispy shallots in this recipe with spring onion due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
